# ApexPlanet User Management System

## Features
- User registration with hashed passwords
- Role-based login (Admin/User)
- CRUD operations (Add, Edit, Delete users)
- Profile picture upload (jpg/png, max 2MB)
- Secure authentication using PHP sessions

## Instructions
1. Install XAMPP and start Apache & MySQL
2. Import database SQL from phpMyAdmin
3. Place project folder in `C:\xampp\htdocs`
4. Access in browser: `http://localhost/apexplanet_task3/`
5. Register users, login, and manage users

